Temperatures and O-ring failures for the launches of the space shuttle

Format

A data frame with 25 observations on the following 4 variables.

flight
a factor with levels 1 2 3 4 41-b 41-c 41-d 41-g 5 51-a 51-b 51-c 51-d 51-f 51-g 51-i 51-j 6 61-a 61-b 61-c 61-i 7 8 9
date
a factor with levels 1/12/86 1/24/85 1/28/86 10/3/85 10/30/85 10/5/84 11/11/82 11/12/81 11/26/85 11/28/83 11/8/84 2/3/84 3/22/82 4/12/81 4/12/85 4/29/85 4/4/83 4/6/84 6/17/85 6/18/83 6/27/82 7/29/85 8/27/85 8/30/83 8/30/84
temp
a numeric vector
Failures
a numeric vector
======= A data frame with 25 observations on the following four variables.
flight
a character variable indicating the flight
date
date of the flight
temp

failures
